messages.message: Hi Brian. It's been forever. I'm doing well. Busy with a baby and a full time job! How are you?
Good. Job hunting. Congrats on the baby. That is awesome. Pass on those genius genes!
What kind of job and where?
Any job, been searching in Phoenix. I might get a contract working on a meditation app.
